sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Assistant as Agent
    participant CtxFactory as IAssistantContextFactory
    participant MW1 as RetrievalMiddleware
    participant MW2 as PromptAugmentationMiddleware
    participant MW3 as GuardrailsMiddleware
    participant Retriever as Vector/Keyword Store
    participant Model as IAssistantModel
    participant Memory as IMemoryService

    User->>Assistant: ReplyAsync(question)

    alt First call only
        Assistant->>Memory: InitializeAsync()
        Memory-->>Assistant: initialized
    end

    Assistant->>CtxFactory: Create(input, history)
    CtxFactory-->>Assistant: AssistantContext

    Note over Assistant,MW1: Request path runs in registration order

    Assistant->>MW1: InvokeAsync(context, next)
    MW1->>Retriever: RetrieveRelevantAsync(query)
    Retriever-->>MW1: topK chunks
    MW1->>MW2: next(context)

    MW2->>MW2: Inject chunks into context.WorkingMessages
    MW2->>MW3: next(context)

    MW3->>MW3: Validate relevance/citation policy
    MW3->>Model: CompleteAsync(context.WorkingMessages)
    Model-->>MW3: AssistantResponse

    Note over Model,Assistant: Response path unwinds in reverse order

    MW3-->>MW2: AssistantResponse
    MW2-->>MW1: AssistantResponse
    MW1-->>Assistant: AssistantResponse

    Assistant->>Assistant: Append User + Assistant messages to History

    opt Memory configured
        Assistant->>Memory: StoreMessageAsync(user)
        Assistant->>Memory: StoreMessageAsync(answer)
    end

    Assistant-->>User: response.Content
